{"type":"message","id":"f92b7c44","parentId":"b2a0561b","timestamp":"2026-06-11T23:19:22.778Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6f0005e533e94124bebab9ec","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-12 04:36\n**状态**: v5.47 Focus 修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v5.47 修复内容\n| # | 问题 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | Zoom 速度缩放 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 2 | Focus 端点错误 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 3 | Focus 固定值 60 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 4 | OSD ns0: 前缀 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 5 | OSD Info 延迟 | ⚠️ 设备特性 |\n\n### 关键发现\n- **Focus ISAPI**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **Focus 格式**: `<FocusData><focus>±60</focus></FocusData>`\n- **固定值**: 官方使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\n\n### 验证命令\n```bash\n# Focus 测试\ncurl -X PUT \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus\" \\\n  --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/xml\" \\\n  -d '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?><FocusData><focus>60</focus></FocusData>'\n\n# AstroHub API\ncurl -X POST \"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"direction\":\"focus-far\",\"speed\":60}'\n```\n\n### 正确端口\n- **AstroHub**: 10280\n- **摄像头 ISAPI**: 80\n- **摄像头 WebSocket**: 7681\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781219962778}}
