{"type":"message","id":"fc27f34d","parentId":"94db9e8a","timestamp":"2026-06-12T00:02:05.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键发现：\n- `loadDeviceImageParams exists: True` ✅\n- `apiGet exists: False` ❌\n\n**问题根源：** `apiGet` 函数在 index.html 的 `<script>` 标签中定义，但没有挂载到 `window` 对象。console.html 中的函数调用 `apiGet()` 时，浏览器可以在同一文档内找到它，但当 Playwright 通过 `page.evaluate()` 在不同上下文调用时，`window.apiGet` 不存在。\n\n实际上在浏览器中正常操作时，函数调用应该能正常工作。问题是用户需要**先连接设备**，然后才会触发 `loadDeviceImageParams`。\n\n让我检查用户实际操作流程：连接设备 → 检查下拉菜单是否填充。\n\n老板你现在看到 `-- 加载中 --` 是因为：\n1. **设备尚未连接** - 或者\n2. **连接后函数没有被正确调用**\n\n让我检查前端是否正确处理了设备连接事件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0ebe42b5ee234470bb5607567790cc08","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1240,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":62003,"output":245,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62248,"cost":{"input":0.062002999999999996,"output":0.0007840000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.062787}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781222516524,"responseId":"cht000d9f96@dx19eb922a93dba5e412"}}
