{"type":"message","id":"1e356f8e","parentId":"6bbcb0c5","timestamp":"2026-06-12T00:58:04.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键发现：`Options: ['-- 加载中 --']`\n\n**`loadDeviceImageParams` 被调用了，但下拉菜单没有更新。** 说明 `apiGet` 在函数执行时不可用。\n\n根本问题：console.html 的 `<script>` 定义函数时，函数体内引用的 `apiGet` 还不存在。虽然函数定义不报错（因为函数体不会立即执行），但调用时 `apiGet` 应该已经存在了（因为 index.html 的 `<script>` 先执行完毕）。\n\n等等——Jinja2 `{% include %}` 是服务端模板，所有 HTML 一起发送到浏览器。浏览器按顺序解析，console.html 的 `<script>` 先执行，然后 index.html 的 `<script>` 执行。\n\n所以当 `loadDeviceImageParams` 被调用时（setTimeout 100ms），`apiGet` 应该已经定义了。\n\n让我直接在浏览器中测试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4bb6d024046f4aaf9c0d4667","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Debug: Check apiGet availability and call loadDeviceImageParams\"\"\"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\ndef debug_test():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        page = browser.new_page()\n        \n        page.goto(\"http://localhost:10280\", timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_load_state(\"networkidle\")\n        time.sleep(1)\n        \n        # Check apiGet\n        r = page.evaluate(\"typeof apiGet\")\n        print(f\"typeof apiGet: {r}\")\n        \n        r = page.evaluate(\"typeof window.apiGet\")\n        print(f\"typeof window.apiGet: {r}\")\n        \n        r = page.evaluate(\"typeof loadDeviceImageParams\")\n        print(f\"typeof loadDeviceImageParams: {r}\")\n        \n        # Try calling apiGet directly\n        try:\n            r = page.evaluate(\"apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/whitebalance')\")\n            print(f\"apiGet result: {r}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"apiGet error: {e}\")\n        \n        # Try calling loadDeviceImageParams\n        try:\n            page.evaluate(\"loadDeviceImageParams('192.168.5.72')\")\n            time.sleep(2)\n            \n            # Check wbMode options\n            options = page.locator(\"#wbMode option\").all_inner_texts()\n            print(f\"wbMode options after load: {options}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"loadDeviceImageParams error: {e}\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    debug_test()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\debug_apiget.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":79776,"output":575,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80351,"cost":{"input":0.079776,"output":0.00184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.081616}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781225861045,"responseId":"cht000d5f23@dx19eb955b35db85e102"}}
