{"type":"message","id":"320ad7ae","parentId":"79fc24fd","timestamp":"2026-06-12T01:50:49.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码逻辑正确。问题：API 返回 `min: 0, max: 100`，但 F 值列表最小是 160。所以 `f.val >= min && f.val <= max` 条件不满足（160 > 100），没有选项被添加。\n\n**根本问题：光圈 API 返回的范围是错误的。**\n\n让我检查实际设备的光圈范围："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e98a42522a324a5391625a2059a8fd35","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --digest -u admin:Nftw1357 \"http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Iris\" 2>$null","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":111681,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111814,"cost":{"input":0.11168099999999999,"output":0.00042560000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11210659999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781229040006,"responseId":"cht000d618b@dx19eb9863500b958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"05388897","parentId":"320ad7ae","timestamp":"2026-06-12T01:50:50.155Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e98a42522a324a5391625a2059a8fd35","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Iris version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<IrisLevel>160</IrisLevel>\r\n<maxIrisLevelLimit>100</maxIrisLevelLimit>\r\n<minIrisLevelLimit>0</minIrisLevelLimit>\r\n</Iris>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":419,"aggregated":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Iris version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<IrisLevel>160</IrisLevel>\r\n<maxIrisLevelLimit>100</maxIrisLevelLimit>\r\n<minIrisLevelLimit>0</minIrisLevelLimit>\r\n</Iris>","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781229050154}}
{"type":"message","id":"b1ae4624","parentId":"05388897","timestamp":"2026-06-12T01:51:13.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"设备返回 `minIrisLevelLimit: 0, maxIrisLevelLimit: 100`，这与海康 ISAPI 文档不符（通常光圈值范围是 160~2200）。\n\n这是设备特性：**该设备的光圈范围是 0~100，不是标准的 F 值范围。**\n\n我需要修改 `loadIris` 函数，支持非标准范围："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_143f615bfc0341748d6bbba9","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":571,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":119076,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119208,"cost":{"input":0.119076,"output":0.0004224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1194984}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781229050157,"responseId":"cht000d39e0@dx19eb9869b9bb9cb212"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a55b30b","parentId":"b1ae4624","timestamp":"2026-06-12T01:51:13.702Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_143f615bfc0341748d6bbba9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function loadIris(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            var ir = r.data;\n            deviceImageParams.iris = ir;\n            \n            var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n            if (irisSelect) {\n                irisSelect.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">-- 选择 --</option>';\n                \n                // F 值映射\n                var fValues = [\n                    {val: 160, label: 'F1.6'},\n                    {val: 200, label: 'F2.0'},\n                    {val: 280, label: 'F2.8'},\n                    {val: 400, label: 'F4.0'},\n                    {val: 560, label: 'F5.6'},\n                    {val: 800, label: 'F8.0'},\n                    {val: 1100, label: 'F11'},\n                    {val: 1600, label: 'F16'},\n                    {val: 2200, label: 'F22'}\n                ];\n                \n                var min = ir.min || 160;\n                var max = ir.max || 2200;\n                var current = ir.current_level || 160;\n                \n                fValues.forEach(function(f) {\n                    if (f.val >= min && f.val <= max) {\n                        var opt = document.createElement('option');\n                        opt.value = f.val;\n                        opt.textContent = f.label;\n                        if (f.val === current) opt.selected = true;\n                        irisSelect.appendChild(opt);\n                    }\n                });\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[Iris] Load failed:', e);\n        // 设置默认选项\n        var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n        if (irisSelect) {\n            irisSelect.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">-- 选择 --</option>';\n            var fValues = ['F1.6', 'F2.0', 'F2.8', 'F4.0', 'F5.6', 'F8.0', 'F11', 'F16', 'F22'];\n            fValues.forEach(function(f) {\n                irisSelect.innerHTML += '<option value=\"' + f + '\">' + f + '</option>';\n            });\n        }\n    });\n\n[188 more lines in file. Use offset=621 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781229073702}}
{"type":"message","id":"eba9d9e3","parentId":"0a55b30b","timestamp":"2026-06-12T01:51:35.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改 `loadIris` 函数，支持非标准范围（0~100）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0b8a0f03c0514246b44142e2","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"oldText":"function loadIris(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            var ir = r.data;\n            deviceImageParams.iris = ir;\n            \n            var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n            if (irisSelect) {\n                irisSelect.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">-- 选择 --</option>';\n                \n                // F 值映射\n                var fValues = [\n                    {val: 160, label: 'F1.6'},\n                    {val: 200, label: 'F2.0'},\n                    {val: 280, label: 'F2.8'},\n                    {val: 400, label: 'F4.0'},\n                    {val: 560, label: 'F5.6'},\n                    {val: 800, label: 'F8.0'},\n                    {val: 1100, label: 'F11'},\n                    {val: 1600, label: 'F16'},\n                    {val: 2200, label: 'F22'}\n                ];\n                \n                var min = ir.min || 160;\n                var max = ir.max || 2200;\n                var current = ir.current_level || 160;\n                \n                fValues.forEach(function(f) {\n                    if (f.val >= min && f.val <= max) {\n                        var opt = document.createElement('option');\n                        opt.value = f.val;\n                        opt.textContent = f.label;\n                        if (f.val === current) opt.selected = true;\n                        irisSelect.appendChild(opt);\n                    }\n                });\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        console.warn('[Iris] Load failed:', e);","newText":"function loadIris(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            var ir = r.data;\n            deviceImageParams.iris = ir;\n            \n            var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n            if (irisSelect) {\n                irisSelect.innerHTML = '';\n                \n                var min = ir.min || 0;\n                var max = ir.max || 100;\n                var current = ir.current_level || 0;\n                \n                // v5.42: 支持非标准范围 (0~100 或 160~2200)\n                if (max <= 100) {\n                    // 简单数值范围\n                    for (var i = 0; i <= max; i += 10) {\n                        var opt = document.createElement('option');\n                        opt.value = i;\n                        opt.textContent = i;\n                        if (i === current) opt.selected = true;\n                        irisSelect.appendChild(opt);\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    // F 值映射\n                    var fValues = [\n                        {val: 160, label: 'F1.6'},\n                        {val: 200, label: 'F2.0'},\n                        {val: 280, label: 'F2.8'},\n                        {val: 400, label: 'F4.0'},\n                        {val: 560, label: 'F5.6'},\n                        {val: 800, label: 'F8.0'},\n                        {val: 1100, label: 'F11'},\n                        {val: 1600, label: 'F16'},\n                        {val: 2200, label: 'F22'}\n                    ];\n                    fValues.forEach(function(f) {\n                        if (f.val >= min && f.val <= max) {\n                            var opt = document.createElement('option');\n                            opt.value = f.val;\n                            opt.textContent = f.label;\n                            if (f.val === current) opt.selected = true;\n                            irisSelect.appendChild(opt);\n          