{"type":"message","id":"71b988e3","parentId":"a7277827","timestamp":"2026-06-12T02:10:54.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题确认：**\n- `loadDeviceImageParams` 函数存在 ✅\n- `apiGet` 函数存在 ✅\n- 但 `wbMode` 下拉菜单只显示 \"-- 加载中 --\"\n\n**原因：** 设备连接后，`loadDeviceImageParams` 没有被自动调用。需要用户手动点击连接按钮触发。\n\n让我检查用户点击连接按钮的代码流程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-45c4ee57afd34c9a8a9f68fbafa014dd","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1218,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":130759,"output":131,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130890,"cost":{"input":0.130759,"output":0.00041920000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1311782}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781230236635,"responseId":"cht000d19b7@dx19eb9987d43b958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecb71822","parentId":"71b988e3","timestamp":"2026-06-12T02:10:54.953Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-45c4ee57afd34c9a8a9f68fbafa014dd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"modifyIpPrompt(\\'' + (d.mac || '') + '\\',\\'' + (d.ip || '') + '\\')\">修改IP</button>');\r\n            btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"deleteDevice(\\'' + (d.mac || d.ip) + '\\')\">删除</button>');\r\n            return '<div class=\"actions\">' + btns.join('') + '</div>';\r\n        }\r\n        // Device Actions\r\n        function connectDevice(ip) {\r\n            addLog('info', '正在连接设备: ' + ip);\r\n            showToast('info', '正在连接设备...');\r\n            // 先获取 credentials\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials').then(function(creds) {\r\n                var username = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.username : 'admin';\r\n                var password = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.password : '';\r\n                var port = (creds && creds.success) ? (creds.port || 80) : 80;\r\n\r\n                // 再调用 connect API\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', { username: username, password: password, port: port }).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\r\n                        // Set connectedDevice BEFORE refreshDevices\r\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; }) || { ip: ip };\r\n                        window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                            ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n                            mac: dev.mac || '', username: username, password: password, port: port, online: true\r\n                        };\r\n                        if (dev.mac) localStorage.setItem('lastConnectedMac', dev.mac);\r\n                        // Update button immediately\r\n                        if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                        // 动态加载设备图像参数（白平衡、快门、光圈、降噪、锐度、OSD）\r\n                        // 延迟调用确保 apiGet 已定义\r\n                        setTimeout(function() {\r\n                            if (typeof loadDeviceImageParams === 'function') {\r\n                                loadDeviceImageParams(ip);\r\n                            }\r\n                        }, 100);\r\n                        // WASM SDK login (with loading indicator)\r\n                        showToast('info', '正在初始化视频流...');\r\n                        if (window.clickLogin2) { window.clickLogin2(); }\r\n                    } else if (result && result.message && result.message.indexOf('凭证') >= 0) {\r\n                        // credentials 错误，提示用户输入\r\n                        var username2 = prompt(\"请输入用户名:\", \"admin\");\r\n                        if (!username2) return;\r\n                        var password2 = prompt(\"请输入密码:\");\r\n                        if (!password2) return;\r\n                        connectDeviceWithCreds(ip, username2, password2, 80);\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        showToast('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                        addLog('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                    }\r\n                }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                    showToast('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n\n[1277 more lines in file. Use offset=1268 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781230254953}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3880678","parentId":"ecb71822","timestamp":"2026-06-12T02:11:03.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码逻辑正确。问题可能是用户刷新页面后，没有重新连接设备，所以下拉菜单没有填充。\n\n**根本问题：** 页面加载后，下拉菜单默认是 `-- 加载中 --`，只有当用户点击连接设备按钮后，才会调用 `loadDeviceImageParams`。\n\n**解决方案：** 页面加载时，如果有已连接的设备，自动调用加载函数。\n\n现在修复 OSD 和 PTZ 合并为开关样式。先查看当前 OSD 部分的 HTML："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_857a0597158a4fbe8e7c757a","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":225,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":140702,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140851,"cost":{"input":0.140702,"output":0.00047680000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1411788}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781230254963,"responseId":"cht000d25ea@dx19eb998bd63ba60352"}}
